title: Alec Baldwin / Lyme Disease
description: Sean tries to comprehend his "fainting spells." Alec Baldwin (you know who he is!) joins us to talk about east coast ticks and the mysterious Lyme Disease. Dr. Wali's hall of fame proves to be confusing for the guys.
author: info@hazymills.com (Hazy Mills Network)
